INTERVIEW CHEAT SHEET
=========================================================

Primitive -> Class
------------------
Conversion Constructor

Test(int);

↓

Test obj = 10;

=========================================================

Class -> Primitive
------------------

Conversion Operator

operator int();

↓

int x = obj;

=========================================================

Class -> Class
--------------

Method 1:
Conversion Constructor

ClassB(ClassA);

Method 2:
Conversion Operator

operator ClassB();

